cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and information retrieval techniques applied to social media texts. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also presents a novel metric based on Information Theory, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques for geolocation of users, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
